Package: snstransparencia
Title: Client for the Portuguese SNS Transparency API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Diogo", "Queiroz Almeida", , "diogo.queiroz.almeida@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: An R6 client for the Portuguese 'SNS Transparencia' open data
    API. Provides helpers to discover and locally cache the dataset catalogue,
    inspect metadata and fields, validate common query inputs, query small
    filtered record sets, and download filtered exports from the public
    'Opendatasoft' Explore API.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/DBLQA90/snstransparencia,
    https://transparencia.sns.gov.pt/
BugReports: https://github.com/DBLQA90/snstransparencia/issues
Imports:
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    R6,
    rlang
Suggests:
    arrow,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
